# Summary

LabForge MVP focuses on deploying the core infrastructure a small Windows-based organization needs.

It does not attempt to manage every endpoint or replace an IT department. Instead, it provides a repeatable, guided, and automated way to build a functional Windows Server environment with Active Directory, DNS, DHCP, file shares, users, groups, and baseline policies.

The MVP establishes the foundation for future infrastructure management, cybersecurity lab deployment, MSP tooling, and enterprise automation features.
